The '''Trade Commission''' was an organization of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] government on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] that oversaw trade and commerce throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], and mediated disputes in such matters.

